attributes.title: Non-standard Controller - GO! #11
attributes.caption: Non-standard controller
attributes.description: In this week's GO!, with a recommendation from Geoff to use Xbox One, the guys fight to be the first person to get an achievement in a game without using a standard controller.

attributes.title: Find a Collectible - GO! #12
attributes.caption: Find a Collectible
attributes.description: In the 12th episode of GO!, without using the Xbox One, the guys have to find and collect a collectible that goes towards an achievement.

attributes.title: Three Game Over Screens - GO! #13
attributes.caption: Three Game Over Screens
attributes.description: In the 13th episode of GO!, with only using one arcade game the guys have to capture three game over screens to win a pizza sticker.

attributes.title: Beat a Level in Halo - GO! #14
attributes.caption: Beat a level in Halo
attributes.description: In the 14th episode of GO!, without using Halo: Spartan Assault and Spartan Wars, the guys have be the first person to beat any level in Halo.
attributes.display_title: Beat a Level in Halo - GO! #14

attributes.title: Capture a Toilet - GO! #15
attributes.caption: Capture a toilet
attributes.description: In the 15th episode of GO!, the first person to capture a toilet, without playing Duke Nukem Forever, wins this week's sticker. Will there be a pizza party after this episode Watch and find out!

attributes.title: Exploding Barrels - GO! #16
attributes.caption: Exploding Barrels
attributes.description: In the 16th episode of GO!, the first person to explode three different barrels in three different games wins this week's sticker.

attributes.title: Deploy a Parachute - GO! #17
attributes.caption: Deploy a Parachute
attributes.description: It's down to the wire in the 17th episode of GO! This week's winner will be the first person who deploys a parachute without using Grand Theft Auto.

attributes.title: Ten in Ten - GO! #18
attributes.caption: Ten in Ten
attributes.description: GO gets a reset! To win this week's sticker the AH guys have to kill ten enemies, in ten different games.

attributes.title: Stuff in Games - GO! #19
attributes.caption: Stuff in Games
attributes.description: In the 19th episode of GO!, the first person to fly a plane, drive a car, drive a motorcycle, ride a skateboard, fly a spaceship, ride a bicycle, fly a helicopter, drive a tank, and pilot a boat without using the same game twice, wins this week's sticker.

attributes.title: 5 Team Kills in 5 Games - GO! #20
attributes.caption: 5 Team Kills in 5 Games
attributes.description: In the 20th episode of GO!, the first person to get five team kills in five different games wins this week's sticker.

attributes.title: Kill a Shark - GO! #21
attributes.caption: Kill a Shark
attributes.description: In the 21st episode of GO!, the first person to kill a shark wins this week's sticker.

attributes.title: Five Multiplayer Kills - GO! #22
attributes.caption: Five Multiplayer Kills
attributes.description: In the 22nd episode of GO!, the first person to get five multiplayer kills wins this week's sticker!

attributes.title: Kill Five Zombies in Five Games - GO! #23
attributes.caption: Kill Five Different Zombies in Five Different Games
attributes.description: In the 23rd episode of GO!, the first person to kill five different zombies in five different games becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.
attributes.display_title: Kill Five Zombies in Five Games - GO! #23

attributes.title: Three Chests in Three Games - GO! #24
attributes.caption: Open Three Chests in Three Different Games
attributes.description: In the 24th episode of GO!, the first person to open three chests in three different games becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection AND get's a custom controller from The Controller Shop!
attributes.display_title: Three Chests in Three Games - GO! #24

attributes.title: 5 Kills in 5 Different Ways - GO! #25
attributes.caption: 5 Kills in 5 Different Ways
attributes.description: In the 25th episode of GO!, the first person to kill someone with a fist, sword, magic, grenade, and a vehicle in five different games becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: 5 Kills in 5 Different Ways Continued - GO! #26
attributes.caption: 5 Kills in 5 Different Ways Continued
attributes.description: In the 26th episode of GO!, the first person to kill someone with a pistol, ax, tank, bow & arrow, and slingshot in five different games becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.
attributes.display_title: 5 Kills in 5 Different Ways Continued - GO! #26

attributes.title: Come in 1st, 2nd, and 3rd Place - GO! #27
attributes.caption: Come in 1st, 2nd, and 3rd Place
attributes.description: In the 27th episode of GO! (new office edition), the first person to come in first, second, and third place in three different games becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: Kill a Hunter and a Brute - GO! #28
attributes.caption: Kill a Hunter and a Brute
attributes.description: In the 28th episode of GO!, the first person to kill a hunter and a brute with playing Halo only one time becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.
attributes.display_title: Kill a Hunter and a Brute - GO! #28

attributes.title: Fart in a Video Game - GO! #29
attributes.caption: Fart in a Video Game
attributes.description: In the 29th episode of GO!, the first person to fart in a video game becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.
attributes.display_title: Fart in a Video Game - GO! #29

attributes.title: Ground Pound - GO! #30
attributes.caption: Ground Pound
attributes.description: In the 30th episode of GO!, the first person do a ground pound in a video game without using Saints Row becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: Kill a Hunter and a Brute (Again) - GO! #31
attributes.caption: Kill a Hunter and a Brute (Again)
attributes.description: In the 31st episode of GO!, the first person to kill a hunter and a brute in games different to the ones used in Episode 28 becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.
attributes.display_title: Kill a Hunter and a Brute (Again) - GO! #31

attributes.title: Kill 3 Chickens in 3 Games - GO! #32
attributes.caption: Kill 3 Chickens in 3 Different Games
attributes.description: In the 32nd episode of GO!, the first person to kill three chickens in three different games becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: Kill all of the Village People - GO! #33
attributes.caption: Kill all of the Village People
attributes.description: In the 33rd episode of GO!, the first person to kill all the characters of the Village People from the song YMCA in different games becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.
attributes.display_title: Kill all of the Village People - GO! #33

attributes.title: #Selfie - GO! #34
attributes.caption: #Selfie
attributes.description: In the 34th episode of GO!, the first person to take the best selfie in GTA V becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: Highest Score - GO! #35
attributes.caption: Highest Score
attributes.description: In the 35th episode of GO!, the person who gets the highest score with Halo 3's campaign scoring becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: X Games - GO! #36
attributes.caption: X Games
attributes.description: In the 36th episode of GO! (or GO! X Games), the person who does a successful trick and landing on a skateboard, BMX bike, motorcycle, and a car jump becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: Three Player Kills - GO! #37
attributes.caption: Three Player Kills
attributes.description: In the 37th episode of GO!, the first person who gets three player kills in GTA V becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: AH Character Names - GO! #38
attributes.caption: AH Character Names
attributes.description: In the 38th episode of GO!, the first person who plays as three different characters in three different video games who have the same first name as an Achievement Hunter becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: Lions, Tigers, and Bears - GO! #39
attributes.caption: Lions, Tigers, and Bears
attributes.description: In the 39th episode of GO!, the first person who kills a lion, a tiger, and a bear becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: Trophy - GO! #40
attributes.caption: Trophy
attributes.description: In the 40th episode of GO!, the first person who gets a trophy becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: Five States - GO! #41
attributes.caption: Five States
attributes.description: In the 41st episode of GO!, the first person who visits five US states becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: Punch-Out - GO! #42
attributes.caption: Punch-Out
attributes.description: In the 42nd episode of GO!, the first person to punch-out five different people in five different games becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: One Thousand Dollars - GO! #43
attributes.caption: One Thousand Dollars
attributes.description: In the 43rd episode of GO!, the first person to win a thousand dollars gambling becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: Kill a Vampire, Zombie, and Werewolf - GO! #44
attributes.caption: Kill a Vampire, Zombie, and Werewolf
attributes.description: In the 44th episode of GO!, the first person to kill a vampire, a zombie, and a werewolf in three different games (but Castlevania) becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.
attributes.display_title: Kill a Vampire, Zombie, and Werewolf - GO! #44

attributes.title: Beat a Boss Edition - GO! #45
attributes.caption: Beat a Boss Edition
attributes.description: In the 45th episode of GO!, the first person to beat a boss becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: Level Five Edition - GO! #46
attributes.caption: Level Five Edition
attributes.description: In the 46th episode of GO!, the first person to get to level five in three different video games, where one game has to be retail, becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: Deliver a Car Edition - GO! #47
attributes.caption: Deliver a Car Edition
attributes.description: In the 47th episode of GO!, the first person to deliver a car in GTA V becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: Golfing Edition - GO! #48
attributes.caption: Golfing Edition
attributes.description: In the 48th episode of GO!, the first person to get a double bogey, bogey, par, birdie, eagle, hole in one becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: Keith David Edition - GO! #49
attributes.caption: Keith David Edition
attributes.description: In the 49th episode of GO!, the first person to hear Keith David's beautiful voice becomes this week's victor and gets a sticker to add to their collection.

attributes.title: 5 Challenges - GO! #50
attributes.caption: 5 Challenges
attributes.description: In the 50th episode of GO!, everyone is old. Also, Geoff gives the guys 5 challenges, but doesn't tell them which one will earn them a sticker. Let the process of elimination commence!

attributes.title: Highest Score Edition - GO! #51
attributes.caption: Highest Score Edition
attributes.description: It's the 51st episode of GO! This week, the crew has 10 minutes to get the highest score they can. Who will win Who will give up immediately Tune in to find out!

attributes.title: Anniversary Edition - GO! #52
attributes.caption: Anniversary Edition
attributes.description: For the one year anniversary of Go, Geoff throws a curve ball to the gang! This week, two stickers are up for grabs: one for redoing Go episode five and one for recreating episode two (get it). Tune in to find out who gets the stickers!

attributes.title: Destiny - GO! #53
attributes.caption: Destiny
attributes.description: This week, Geoff realizes that the guys just want to play Destiny, so he lets them! The challenge is to be the first to find a Legendary Engram. No gift packages. No buying. Finding. Will they play multiplayer Will they go to the moon Watch to find out!

attributes.title: Destiny #2 - GO! #54
attributes.caption: Destiny #2
attributes.description: Another Destiny week! This time, the challenge is much simpler: be the first to get a kill on every planet (and the moon). Not the reef though, since... well let's not talk about the reef.

attributes.title: Scary Character Edition - GO! #55
attributes.caption: Scary Character Edition
attributes.description: In this week's completely relevant Go, Geoff tasks the group with creating the scariest character they can in a player creator. The winner will be selected with the power of democracy (voting). Who will get the most votes Will Ray try Tune in to find out!

attributes.title: Halo 3 - GO! #56
attributes.caption: Halo 3
attributes.description: In this week's Go, it's a race to beat the last level of Halo 3! Watch as the gang drives, falls and... falls some more!

attributes.title: Lego Edition - GO! #57
attributes.caption: Lego Edition
attributes.description: This week, the gang has a task much greater than any video game: real life! The first one to accurately build a Lego set, wins!

attributes.title: Kill a Whale Edition - GO! #58
attributes.caption: Kill a Whale Edition
attributes.description: Geoff wants the gang to kill a whale in GTAV. Geoff thought it wouldn't take long. Geoff was wrong.

attributes.title: Kill an Eagle Edition - GO! #59
attributes.caption: Kill an Eagle Edition
attributes.description: This week, the task is as un-American as possible: kill an eagle inFar Cry 4. The first to do it will earn a sticker. The last... well noone cares about them because this is America.

attributes.title: Lone Wolf Edition - GO! #60
attributes.caption: Lone Wolf Edition
attributes.description: This week, the gang celebrates the Master Chief Collection by not playing it and instead playing Halo Reach. Whoever lasts the longest in Lone Wolf wins a sticker!!!

attributes.title: Holiday Edition - GO! #61
attributes.caption: Holiday Edition
attributes.description: This week's Go! is a test of holiday cheer! Who will be the first to find either a snowman, a Christmas tree, or a wrapped present in a video game! Sorry Kwanza.

attributes.title: Drinking Edition - GO! #62
attributes.caption: Drinking Edition
attributes.description: In GO! this week, Geoff tasks the gang with a New Year's tradition: drinking. First to get drunk in a video game wins!
